Directory layout:

 * protobuf:

     Clone of:
     http://protobuf.googlecode.com/files/protobuf-2.0.0beta.tar.gz

     ... but with Perl support added.  That is, it auto-generates
     really ugly Perl.

 * perl

     hand-written Perl.  for CPAN.  necessary dependency for the
     aforementioned ugly auto-generated Perl.
